name: Devin Sanford
summary:
Devin Sanford is a 32-year-old man who stands at 6'0". He identifies as straight and goes by the pronouns He/Him/His. Currently residing in Los Angeles, California, Devin hails from Chicago, Illinois. He works as a Software Developer in the technology industry and has a graduate degree from New York University. 

Devin values kindness and academic knowledge. In his free time, he enjoys cycling, cooking, reading, and coding. Fluent in English and Spanish, he is of Black African descent and is an atheist with liberal political views.

He has categorically expressed his intention towards long-term dating and prefers monogamous relationships. Although he currently doesn't have any children, he would like to in the future. A dog owner, he isactive physically, is an occasional drinker, and does not smoke or use marijuana or other drugs.

Devin is open to connecting with a straight woman who ranges in age from 26 to 34 and stands anywhere between 5'4" to 6'0". His potential match should have no children but be open to having some in the future. In terms of lifestyle, he desires a non-smoking, active woman who enjoys an occasional drink but abstains from marijuana and drugs.
